#REPOST @cormega with @get__repost__app  Hip Hop 50 Year Anniversary •Since it’s Friday I have to throw this up because Friday was the day the new videos debuted. In my observation there’s only 5 things that would make drug dealers stop what their doing and leave. 1- the police obviously 2- Video Music Box 3- Michael Jackson world premiere 4-The Wire and 5- baddies. Anyway back to the story. So every Friday you knew to expect something. You never knew what it was because sometimes Ralph would be at events so you might see artist on stage and get caught up in that. Another thing Ralph made popular was the shout out. (I didn’t say he created it for the reading comprehension challenged that always want to debate not today it’s too hot.)He would be in the club and ask someone do they want to give a shout out. And you’d see regular people give shoutouts. That week the regular person was lit because people seen them on Video Music Box. “ Video Music Box longevity is unprecedented. It outlasted everything and was the blueprint for MTV Rap and Rap City. Every rapper from the 80s and 90s especially East coast should put some respect on Ralph McDaniels and Video Music Box because we ain’t even know how some of you look until you got your video on Video Music Box. 
#ralphmcdaniels #videomusicbox #repostandroid #repostw10

Well said by one of the legends in the game!🤴🏾🎤💪🏿💯 Uncle Ralph is the "Blueprint " !!💯🎤🎥 #vmb40 #hiphop50
